{"tid":415233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［美帝反加獨］特朗普：西班牙應維持統一 西首相：公投無效","createTime":"2017-09-26T22:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T04:10:06.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"620e240243e5aa4bf7cc0e08deefdc7b766a3b22","tid":415233,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T22:49:20.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普在白宮，會見西班牙首相拉霍伊，談及加泰羅尼亞將於星期日舉行獨立公投。特朗普形容西班牙是偉大國家，應維持統一，認為加泰羅尼亞民眾，應該讓當地繼續留在西班牙。拉霍伊強調今次獨立公投瘋狂，由於選舉委員會未能監察公投過程，即使舉行亦會視作不合法。<br />\n<br />\n兩人又談及反恐問題，特朗普指美國與西班牙是反恐盟友，兩國將共同對抗威脅人類的邪惡行徑，並繼續聯手切斷恐怖分子的資金來源。他又感謝西班牙參與打擊伊斯蘭國的聯盟，協助伊拉克訓練三萬多名保安部隊成員。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=966663&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fpage%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D966663%26csid%3D261_367&d=ET79mwu14G5d3JvAXnBCiAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=c08d46de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=966663&amp;csid=261_367</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/064752_6776e5539e5f11d2ce916ad32a6c9d50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F064752_6776e5539e5f11d2ce916ad32a6c9d50.jpg&h=6592d0ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西班牙首相咁急赴美就知美國一句勝過任何反獨政策"},{"pid":"2a576d945ba3cd2dccef069d8fc5cf94fda6f71e","tid":415233,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T00:33:34.000Z","msg":"美國一句定特朗普一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae06cc07fc05ab02fedd18da314e74e0a0d28e1","tid":415233,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:10:06.000Z","msg":"特朗普不代表美帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}